    <item>
      <title>沃尔沃将收购 Northvolt 电池合资企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/volvo-car-to-take-ownership-of-northvolt-battery-joint-venture</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔沃汽车公司 (Volvo Car AB) 正在与陷入财务困境的 Northvolt AB 成立合资企业，在瑞典西海岸建造一家工厂，这凸显了电动汽车市场扩大电池生产规模所面临的重大挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/volvo-car-to-take-ownership-of-northvolt-battery-joint-venture</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:26:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区经济增长超出预期，德国避开衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/french-economy-gathers-speed-with-boost-from-paris-olympics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区经济第三季度扩张势头强于预期——甚至德国也避免了人们普遍预计会持续的经济衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/french-economy-gathers-speed-with-boost-from-paris-olympics</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国锌业因董事长拟募资 18 亿美元而股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/korea-zinc-shares-sink-30-after-announcing-new-share-sale-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国锌业公司董事长计划以大幅折价发行股票，令市场大吃一惊，随后该公司股价周三一度暴跌 30%，至每日涨停板，市值蒸发 70 亿美元，这是该公司长达数月的控制权争夺战中出现的最新转折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/korea-zinc-shares-sink-30-after-announcing-new-share-sale-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 02:42:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价在连续两天下跌后小幅走高，焦点是中东问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在连续两天下跌后小幅走高，交易员们正在权衡中东局势发展以及 OPEC+ 增加供应的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 23:31:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关键事件发生前谨慎情绪笼罩美国期货市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统大选和美联储政策决定公布前几天，交易员们正在等待包括大型科技股收益和关键经济报告在内的一系列风险，美国股指期货难以获得支撑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 22:28:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能芯片增长未能激发投资者兴趣，AMD 股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/amd-forecast-falls-short-suggesting-a-slower-pace-of-ai-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超威半导体公司 (Advanced Micro Devices Inc.) 股价在尾盘交易中下跌，原因是该芯片制造商的营收预测不及分析师预期，这表明其人工智能销售增长速度低于一些人的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/amd-forecast-falls-short-suggesting-a-slower-pace-of-ai-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 20:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
